See below&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
From Wilkesboro and the Triad:&lt;br /&gt;
Take US HWY 421 N 6.7 miles west of Blue Ridge Parkway&lt;br /&gt;
Right at light on Old US HWY 421 before supermarket&lt;br /&gt;
Travel one mile to Roby Greene Road and take a right&lt;br /&gt;
see below:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
From Roby Greene Road:&lt;br /&gt;
After less than a quarter mile, you will see a huge lumberyard on your left&lt;br /&gt;
The left-hand entrance is only about 100 yards beyond the lumberyard.&lt;br /&gt;
Follow the driveway onto the property, bearing left.&lt;br /&gt;
Drive slowly and be careful of cyclists warming up and racing across the driveway!&lt;br /&gt;
Parking is in the field ahead and to your right.&lt;br /&gt;
Registration is in the center of the grandstands through the fence and to your right.&lt;br /&gt;
